  OBJECT-PROPERTIES

    Date=;
    Time=;

                TableData 25=r,
                TableData 379=r,
                TableData 380=r,

               NOR=konomisk prosjektoversikt;
               SVE=Finansiell ”versikt projekt];
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  IF PeriodFilter = '' THEN
                    ERROR(Text002);
                  //160412 ITERO.PEPF
                  CompanyInfo.GET;
                  //160412 ITERO.PEPF
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 1100525002;;DataItem;                  ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               Job.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilter);
                               Job.SETRANGE("Cumulation Filter", 0D, Job.GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter"));

                               Job.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));

                               TEMPControlProjectCostObject.DELETEALL;
                             END;
                              }

    { 1100525001;1;Column;COMPANYNAME        ;
               SourceExpr=CompanyInfo.Name }

    { 1100525000;1;Column;REPORTNAME         ;
               SourceExpr=GetReportName }

    { 1100525005;1;Column;REPORTFILTER       ;
               SourceExpr=GetReportFilter }

    { 1100525101;1;Column;DPA_GetFiltersFltrGrp7;
               SourceExpr=Job.DPA_GetFiltersFltrGrp(7) }

    { 1100525004;0;DataItem;                 ;
               DataItemTable=Table11072003;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(No.)
                                 ORDER(Ascending);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilter);
                               SETRANGE("Cumulation Filter", 0D, GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter"));

                               Permissions.CostControlReports(Job);

                               DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));

                               //PopulateTemptable(Job."No.");
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  BuildCostControl;

                                  DeterminePrognosisDate.DetermineBothDates(Job);
                                  "Prognosis Filter" := GETRANGEMAX("Prognosis Filter");
                                  PrevPrognosisFilter := GETRANGEMAX(PrevPrognosisFilter);

                                  DetermineProgressDate.DetermineBothDates(Job,FALSE);
                                  "Progress Filter" := GETRANGEMAX("Progress Filter");
                                  PrevProgressFilter := GETRANGEMAX(PrevProgressFilter);


                                  PopulateTemptable(Job);
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No. }

    { 1100525062;1;Column;TABLECAPTION_Job   ;
               SourceExpr=TABLECAPTION }

    { 1100525027;1;Column;No_Job             ;
               SourceExpr=Job."No." }

               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr=Job."Project Contract Amount" }

               IncludeCaption=Yes;

    { 1100525032;1;Column;EndingDate_Job     ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr=Job."Ending Date" }

    { 1100525033;1;Column;ActualCosts_Job    ;
               SourceExpr=Job."Actual Costs" }

    { 1100525006;1;DataItem;CopyLoop         ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=FILTER(1|2));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF (NOT PrintSummary AND NOT PrintDetails) THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CASE TRUE OF
                                    (PrintSummary AND PrintDetails):
                                      IF NOT (Number IN [1,2]) THEN
                                        CurrReport.SKIP;
                                    (PrintSummary AND NOT PrintDetails):
                                      IF Number = 2 THEN
                                        CurrReport.SKIP;
                                    (NOT PrintSummary AND PrintDetails):
                                      IF Number = 1 THEN
                                        CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  END;
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1100525063;2;Column;Number_CopyLoop    ;
               SourceExpr=Number }

    { 1100525007;2;DataItem;ControlProjectCostObject;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF (NOT PrintDetails) AND (CopyLoop.Number = 2) THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;

                               //ITERO.MK >>
                               CLEAR(TotalRevenue);
                               CLEAR(TotalCost);
                               CLEAR(TotalPrognosisRevenueDec);
                               CLEAR(TotalPrognosisCostDec);
                               //ITERO.MK <<
                               SETRANGE(Number,1,TEMPControlProjectCostObject.COUNT);
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  CostComponent@1000000000 : Record 11012012;
                                BEGIN
                                  IF Number = 1 THEN
                                    TEMPControlProjectCostObject.FIND('-')
                                  ELSE
                                    TEMPControlProjectCostObject.NEXT;

                                  SortKey := 2;
                                  //CostType := TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component";
                                  TEMPControlProjectCostObject.CALCFIELDS(Description);

                                  CASE TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" OF

                                      '1': CostType := LaborText;
                                      '2': CostType := MaterialText;
                                      '3': CostType := SubcontractiongText;
                                      '4': CostType := PlantText;
                                      '5': CostType := SundryText;
                                      '6': BEGIN
                                        CostType := RevenuesText;
                                        SortKey := 1;
                                      END;
                                  END;

                                  Job.COPYFILTER("Period Filter", TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Period Filter");
                                  Job.COPYFILTER("Cumulation Filter", TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cumulation Filter");
                                  Job.COPYFILTER("Prognosis Filter", TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Prognosis Filter");
                                  Job.COPYFILTER("Progress Filter", TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Progress Filter");
                                  TEMPControlProjectCostObject.SETRANGE("Purchase Action Filter");

                                  CostControlManagement.CalcFieldsCostObj(TEMPControlProjectCostObject);
                                  TotalBudgetDec := TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Budget;
                                  ActualCostDec := TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Actual Costs";
                                  PurchBudgetDec := TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Purchase Budget";
                                  PrognosisDec := TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Prognosis;

                                  BudgetNotOnPurchaseActionDec := TotalBudgetDec - PurchBudgetDec;

                                  TotCostDec := CostControlManagement.TotCostCostObj(TEMPControlProjectCostObject, FALSE);

                                  CostControlManagement.AllowedAndPurchCostObj(
                                    TEMPControlProjectCostObject, AllowedDec, AllowedHoursDec, PrevAllowedDec,
                                    PrevAllowedHoursDec, PurchaseDec, PurchResultDec, PurchCostDec,
                                    ActualPurchResultDec, TotPurchResultDec, TRUE);

                                  MatchedToOrdersDec := PurchaseDec - TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Open (Purchase)";

                                  PurchResultDec := PurchResultDec - (TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Risc Coverage" - TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Risc Coverage Withdraw");

                                  PrognEndResultDec := CostControlManagement.PrognEndResultCostObj(TEMPControlProjectCostObject, FALSE);

                                  TEMPControlProjectCostObject.SETFILTER("Purchase Action Filter", '%1', '');
                                  ActualNotOnPurchaseActionDec := CostControlManagement.TotCostCostObj(TEMPControlProjectCostObject, TRUE);

                                  RemainingAmntDec := TotalBudgetDec - PurchBudgetDec - ActualNotOnPurchaseActionDec;

                                  Job.COPYFILTER(PrevPrognosisFilter, TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Prognosis Filter");
                                  TEMPControlProjectCostObject.CALCFIELDS(Prognosis);
                                  PrevPrognDec := TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Prognosis;
                                  IF PrevPrognDec <> 0 THEN
                                    PrognDifferenceDec := PrognosisDec - PrevPrognDec
                                  ELSE
                                    PrognDifferenceDec := 0;

                                  IF ProjectCostObject.GET(TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Project No.", TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object") THEN BEGIN
                                    TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Description := ProjectCostObject.Name;
                                    TEMPControlProjectCostObject.MODIFY;
                                  END ELSE IF CostComponent.GET(TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object") THEN BEGIN
                                    IF TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object" = '3K' THEN
                                      TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Description := CostComponent.Description + ' (9220-9255)'
                                    ELSE IF TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object" = '4T' THEN
                                      TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Description := CostComponent.Description + ' (9260-9266)'
                                    ELSE
                                      TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Description := CostComponent.Description;
                                    TEMPControlProjectCostObject.MODIFY;
                                  END;

                                  //ITERO.MK >>
                                  RevenueDec := GetRevenue(TEMPControlProjectCostObject);
                                  ContractAmountDec := GetContractAmount(TEMPControlProjectCostObject);
                                  TEMPControlProjectCostObject.CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Total Cost");
                                  PrognosisTotalCostDec := GetPrognosisCost(TEMPControlProjectCostObject);//TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Prognosis Total Cost";
                                  PrognosisRevenueDec := GetPrognosisRevenue(TEMPControlProjectCostObject);
                                  DiffEstimateRevenueDec := RevenueDec - ContractAmountDec;
                                  DiffEstimateCosteDec := ActualCostDec - TotalBudgetDec;
                                  DiffPrognosisRevenueDec := RevenueDec - PrognosisRevenueDec;
                                  DiffPrognosisCostDec := ActualCostDec - PrognosisTotalCostDec;
                                  TotalRevenue += RevenueDec;
                                  TotalCost += ActualCostDec;
                                  BalanceDec := TotalRevenue - TotalCost;
                                  TotalPrognosisRevenueDec += PrognosisRevenueDec;
                                  TotalPrognosisCostDec += PrognosisTotalCostDec;
                                  //ITERO.MK <<
                                  //ITERO.MK >>
                                  //BalanceDec := RevenueDec - ActualCostDec;
                                  //MarginDec := TotalPrognosisRevenueDec - TotalPrognosisCostDec;
                                  //ITERO.MK <<
                                END;

               DataItemLinkReference=Job }

    { 1100525111;3;Column;SortKey            ;
               SourceExpr=SortKey }

    { 1100525045;3;Column;ActualNotOnPurchaseActionDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=ActualNotOnPurchaseActionDec }

    { 1100525046;3;Column;RemainingAmntDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=RemainingAmntDec }

    { 1100525047;3;Column;PrognosisDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=PrognosisDec }

    { 1100525048;3;Column;PrognEndResultDec_ControlProjectCostObject;

    { 1100525050;3;Column;PrognDifferenceDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=PrognDifferenceDec }

    { 1100285500;3;Column;RevenueDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=RevenueDec }

    { 1100285507;3;Column;ContractAmountDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=ContractAmountDec }

    { 1100285509;3;Column;PrognosisRevenueDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=PrognosisRevenueDec }

    { 1100285508;3;Column;PrognosisTotalCostDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=PrognosisTotalCostDec }

    { 1100285513;3;Column;DiffEstimateRevenueDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=DiffEstimateRevenueDec }

    { 1100285514;3;Column;DiffEstimateCosteDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=DiffEstimateCosteDec }

    { 1100285515;3;Column;DiffPrognosisRevenueDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=DiffPrognosisRevenueDec }

    { 1100285516;3;Column;DiffPrognosisCostDec_ControlProjectCostObject;
               SourceExpr=DiffPrognosisCostDec }

    { 1100525008;2;DataItem;Summary          ;
               DataItemTable=Table2000000026;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Number)
                                 ORDER(Ascending)
                                 WHERE(Number=CONST(1));
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               IF (NOT PrintSummary) OR (CopyLoop.Number = 2) THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=BEGIN
                                  CalcProject;
                                  //ITERO.MK >>
                                  BalanceDec := TotalRevenue - TotalCost;
                                  MarginDec := TotalPrognosisRevenueDec - TotalPrognosisCostDec;

                                  IF (TotalPrognosisRevenueDec = 0) AND (TotalPrognosisCostDec = 0) THEN
                                    MarginProcent := 0
                                  ELSE IF TotalPrognosisRevenueDec > 0 THEN
                                    MarginProcent := (TotalPrognosisRevenueDec -TotalPrognosisCostDec)/TotalPrognosisRevenueDec
                                  ELSE
                                    MarginProcent := -1;

                                  //ITERO.MK <<
                                END;
                                 }

    { 1100525064;3;Column;Number_Summary     ;
               SourceExpr=Number }

    { 1100525030;3;Column;PrognosisCostPlustoInvoice_Summary;
               SourceExpr=Prognosis."Cost Plus to Invoice" }

    { 1100525051;3;Column;ExtensionToInvoice_Summary;

    { 1100285541;2;DataItem;                 ;
               DataItemTable=Table11072005;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Job No.,Cost Type,Global Dimension 2 Code);
               OnPreDataItem=BEGIN
                               //IF (NOT PrintTransactions) OR (CopyLoop.Number = 1) THEN
                               //  CurrReport.BREAK;
                               IF NOT PrintTransactions THEN
                                 CurrReport.BREAK;

                               IF Job."Single/Main/Sub Project" = Job."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                 SETRANGE("Main Project No.", Job."No.")
                               ELSE
                                 SETRANGE("Job No.", Job."No.");

                               SETFILTER("Posting Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  DimVal@1100285501 : Record 349;
                                  DimMgt@1100285500 : Codeunit 408;
                                BEGIN
                                  DimMgt.GetDimValueRec(2, "Global Dimension 2 Code", DimVal, FALSE, "Job No.");
                                  CostObjectDesc := DimVal.Name;

                                  NameTxt := '';
                                  LevCustCode := '';

                                  CASE "Entry Type" OF
                                    "Entry Type"::Usage:
                                      BEGIN
                                        LevCustCode := "Vendor No.";
                                        GetVendorName(NameTxt);
                                      END;
                                    "Entry Type"::Sale:
                                      BEGIN
                                        LevCustCode := Principal;
                                        CALCFIELDS("Principal Name");
                                        NameTxt := STRSUBSTNO('%1',"Principal Name");
                                      END;
                                  END;

                                  //ITERO.MK 150831 >>
                                  IF ("Total Cost (LCY)" = 0) AND ("Total Price (LCY)" = 0) THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  //ITERO.MK 150831 <<

                                  IF "Cost Type" = "Cost Type"::Revenues THEN
                                    SortKeyTransactions := 1
                                  ELSE
                                    SortKeyTransactions := 2;
                                END;

               DataItemLinkReference=Job }

    { 1000000005;3;Column;SortKeyTransactions;
               SourceExpr=SortKeyTransactions }

    { 1100285548;ProjectTransactionsCaption;

    { 1100285549;ProjectDetailsCaption;
                                CaptionML=[ENU=Project Details;
                                           NOR=Prosjektdetaljer;
                                           SVE=Projektdetaljer] }
    { 1100285550;ProjectOverviewCaption;
                                CaptionML=[ENU=Project Overview;

                                           SVE=Projekt”versikt] }
    { 1100285100;CostTypeCaption;

  }
  CODE
  {
    VAR
      CostType@1100285100 : Text;
      Prognosis@1100525033 : Record 11012034;
      ProjectCostObject@1100525058 : Record 11012065;
      Permissions@1100525057 : Codeunit 11012026;
      DetermineProgressDate@1100525055 : Codeunit 11012014;
      DeterminePrognosisDate@1100525054 : Codeunit 11012029;
      CostControlManagement@1100525053 : Codeunit 11012006;
      DateSelectionManagement@1100525060 : Codeunit 11130005;
      PeriodFilter@1100525049 : Text[250];
      PurchaseDec@1100525047 : Decimal;
      PurchCostDec@1100525046 : Decimal;
      PurchResultDec@1100525045 : Decimal;
      RemainingAmntDec@1100525044 : Decimal;
      PrintSummary@1100525043 : Boolean;
      PrintDetails@1100525042 : Boolean;
      ExtensionToInvoice@1100525041 : Decimal;
      CostPlusToInvoice@1100525040 : Decimal;
      ExtensionApproved@1100525039 : Decimal;
      OptionToInvoice@1100525038 : Decimal;
      OptionApproved@1100525037 : Decimal;
      InstallmentsInvoiced@1100525036 : Decimal;
      ExtensionsInvoiced@1100525035 : Decimal;
      CostPlusInvoiced@1100525034 : Decimal;
      ProjectDays@1100525032 : Decimal;
      CumDays@1100525031 : Decimal;
      PercTime@1100525030 : Decimal;
      PercTurnOver@1100525029 : Decimal;
      InstallmentsToReceive@1100525028 : Decimal;
      CostPlusToReceive@1100525027 : Decimal;
      VendorBalance@1100525026 : Decimal;
      LaborCost@1100525025 : Decimal;
      CostPerc@1100525024 : Decimal;
      LaborPerc@1100525023 : Decimal;
      PrevPrognDec@1100525022 : Decimal;
      TotCostDec@1100525021 : Decimal;
      DatFilterStart@1100525020 : Date;
      DatFilterEnd@1100525019 : Date;
      TotalBudgetDec@1100525018 : Decimal;
      ActualCostDec@1100525017 : Decimal;
      PurchBudgetDec@1100525016 : Decimal;
      MatchedToOrdersDec@1100525015 : Decimal;
      BudgetNotOnPurchaseActionDec@1100525014 : Decimal;
      ActualNotOnPurchaseActionDec@1100525013 : Decimal;
      PrognosisDec@1100525012 : Decimal;
      PrognEndResultDec@1100525011 : Decimal;
      PrognDifferenceDec@1100525010 : Decimal;
      PayedInstallments@1100525009 : Decimal;
      PayedCostPlus@1100525008 : Decimal;
      AllowedDec@1100525007 : Decimal;
      AllowedHoursDec@1100525006 : Decimal;

      ActualPurchResultDec@1100525003 : Decimal;
      TotPurchResultDec@1100525002 : Decimal;
      Text002@1100525000 : TextConst 'ENU=Select Accumulated at Date on option tab.;NOR=Velg Akkumulert t.o.m. p† valgfanen;SVE=V„lj Ackumulerat t.o.m. p† alternativfliken.';
      "***"@1100285500 : Integer;

      ContractAmountDec@1100285502 : Decimal;

      DPAFilterGroup7@1100285515 : Text[250];

      TEMPControlProjectCostObject@1100285522 : TEMPORARY Record 11012047;
      LaborText@1100285101 : TextConst 'ENU=Labor;NOR=Arbeidskraf;SVE=Arbetskraft';
      MaterialText@1100285102 : TextConst 'ENU=Material;NOR=Materiale;SVE=Material';
      SubcontractiongText@1100285103 : TextConst 'ENU=Subcontractiong;NOR=Underentrepen›r;SVE=Underentreprenad';

      SundryText@1100285105 : TextConst 'ENU=Sundry;NOR=Diverse;SVE=Diverse';

      SortKeyTransactions@1000000001 : Integer;
      PrintTransactionsEditable@1000000003 : Boolean INDATASET;
      CompanyInfo@1100285107 : Record 79;

    PROCEDURE GetReportName@1100525003() : Text;
    BEGIN
      EXIT(DELSTR(CurrReport.OBJECTID, 1, STRPOS(CurrReport.OBJECTID, ' ')));
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetReportFilter@1100525000() : Text;
    BEGIN
      IF Job.GETFILTERS <> '' THEN
        EXIT(STRSUBSTNO('%1: %2', Job.TABLECAPTION, Job.GETFILTERS));
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcProject@1100485000();
    VAR
      ExtensionContract@1100485000 : Record 11012004;
      Option@1100485003 : Record 11012502;
      JobLedgerEntry@1100485004 : Record 11072005;
      ProjectInstallment@1100485005 : Record 11012018;
      CustLedgerEntry@1100485006 : Record 21;
      VendorLedgerEntry@1100485008 : Record 25;
      PercDec@1100485007 : Decimal;
      PayedAmnt@1100485001 : Decimal;
      PayedPerc@1100485011 : Decimal;
      ControlProjectCostType@1100485012 : Record 11012046;
      MainProjFilter@1100485014 : Text[30];
      ProjFilter@1100485013 : Text[30];
    BEGIN
      ExtensionToInvoice := 0;
      ExtensionApproved := 0;
      OptionApproved := 0;
      OptionToInvoice := 0;
      ExtensionsInvoiced := 0;
      InstallmentsInvoiced := 0;
      CostPlusInvoiced := 0;
      VendorBalance := 0;
      PayedInstallments := 0;
      InstallmentsToReceive := 0;
      //ik heb het gebruik van de nieuwe variabelen ProjFilter en MainProjFilter overigens niet
      //van commentaar voorzien
      IF Job."Single/Main/Sub Project" <> Job."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN BEGIN
        MainProjFilter := '';
        ProjFilter := Job."No.";
      END ELSE BEGIN
        MainProjFilter := Job."No.";
        ProjFilter := '';
      END;
      Job.SETFILTER("Project Filter", ProjFilter);
      Job.CALCFIELDS(
        "Project Contract Amount", "Contract Amount", Budget, "Actual Costs",
        "Budget Hours (Entire Project)", "Actual Hours", "Open Hours");

      ExtensionToInvoice := 0;
      ExtensionApproved := 0;
      ExtensionContract.RESET;
      ExtensionContract.SETFILTER("Project No.", ProjFilter);
      ExtensionContract.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", MainProjFilter);
      ExtensionContract.SETFILTER("Contract Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
      IF ExtensionContract.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          IF ExtensionContract.Status = ExtensionContract.Status::"Invoicing Allowed" THEN
            ExtensionToInvoice := ExtensionToInvoice + ExtensionContract."Contract Amount (LCY)";
          IF ExtensionContract.Status = ExtensionContract.Status::Order THEN
            ExtensionApproved :=  ExtensionApproved + ExtensionContract."Contract Amount (LCY)";
        UNTIL ExtensionContract.NEXT = 0;
      END;

      OptionToInvoice := 0;
      OptionApproved := 0;
      Option.RESET;
      Option.SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.","Plot No.",Group,"Sub Group","Contract Date");
      Option.SETFILTER("Project No.", ProjFilter);
      Option.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", MainProjFilter);
      Option.SETFILTER("Contract Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
      Option.SETFILTER(Status, '%1..%2', Option.Status::Order, Option.Status::Invoice);
      IF Option.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          CASE Option.Status OF
            Option.Status::Order:
              OptionApproved := OptionApproved + Option."Contract Amount";
            Option.Status::Invoice:
              OptionToInvoice := OptionToInvoice + Option."Contract Amount";
          END;
        UNTIL Option.NEXT = 0;
      END;

      JobLedgerEntry.RESET;
      JobLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Job No.","Posting Date");
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Job No.", ProjFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", MainProjFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Posting Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Entry Type", JobLedgerEntry."Entry Type"::Sale);
      JobLedgerEntry.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));
      IF JobLedgerEntry.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          ProjectInstallment.RESET;
          IF ProjectInstallment.GET(JobLedgerEntry."Job No.",JobLedgerEntry.Principal,
                                 JobLedgerEntry."Plot No.",JobLedgerEntry."Installment No.") THEN BEGIN
            IF (ProjectInstallment."Extension Contract" <> '') OR (ProjectInstallment.Option <> '') THEN
              ExtensionsInvoiced := ExtensionsInvoiced - JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)"
            ELSE
              InstallmentsInvoiced := InstallmentsInvoiced - JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)";
          END ELSE
            CostPlusInvoiced -= JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)"
        UNTIL JobLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;
      END;

      IF (Job."Starting Date" <> 0D) AND (Job."Ending Date" <> 0D) THEN BEGIN
        ProjectDays := Job."Ending Date" - Job."Starting Date";
        CumDays := Job."Ending Date" - Job.GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter");
        IF ProjectDays <> 0 THEN
          PercTime := 100 - (CumDays / ProjectDays * 100) ;
      END;

      IF Job.Budget <> 0 THEN
        CostPerc := 100 * Job."Actual Costs" / Job.Budget
      ELSE
        CostPerc := 0;

      IF Job."Budget Hours (Entire Project)" <> 0  THEN
        LaborPerc := (Job."Actual Hours" + Job."Open Hours") / Job."Budget Hours (Entire Project)" * 100
      ELSE
        LaborPerc := 0;

      IF (Job."Contract Amount" + ExtensionToInvoice + ExtensionApproved + OptionToInvoice + OptionApproved) = 0 THEN
        PercTurnOver := 0
      ELSE
        PercTurnOver := ((InstallmentsInvoiced + ExtensionsInvoiced) /
                        (Job."Contract Amount" + ExtensionToInvoice + ExtensionApproved + OptionToInvoice + OptionApproved)) * 100;

      VendorBalance := 0;
      JobLedgerEntry.RESET;
      JobLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Job No.","Document No.","Posting Date");
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Job No.", ProjFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", MainProjFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Entry Type", JobLedgerEntry."Entry Type"::Usage);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE(Surcharge, FALSE);
      JobLedgerEntry.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));
      IF JobLedgerEntry.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          VendorLedgerEntry.RESET;
          VendorLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.");
          VendorLedgerEntry.SETFILTER(
            "Document Type", '%1|%2', VendorLedgerEntry."Document Type"::Invoice, VendorLedgerEntry."Document Type"::"Credit Memo");
          VendorLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Document No.", JobLedgerEntry."Document No.");
          VendorLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Posting Date", '..%1', Job.GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter"));
          IF VendorLedgerEntry.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
            REPEAT
              VendorLedgerEntry.CALCFIELDS("Original Amt. (LCY)", "Remaining Amt. (LCY)");
              PayedAmnt := VendorLedgerEntry."Original Amt. (LCY)" - VendorLedgerEntry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)";
              IF VendorLedgerEntry."Original Amt. (LCY)" <> 0 THEN
                PayedPerc := (PayedAmnt / VendorLedgerEntry."Original Amt. (LCY)") * 100
              ELSE
                PayedPerc := 0;
              VendorBalance := VendorBalance + (JobLedgerEntry."Total Cost (LCY)" / 100) * PayedPerc;
            UNTIL VendorLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;
          END;
        UNTIL JobLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;
      END;

      PayedInstallments := 0;
      InstallmentsToReceive := 0;
      PayedCostPlus := 0;
      CostPlusToReceive := 0;
      JobLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Project Invoice", "Installment Invoice", "Job No.", Principal, "Installment No.");
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Project Invoice", TRUE);
      //JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Installment Invoice", TRUE);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Job No.", ProjFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Main Project No.", MainProjFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Entry Type", JobLedgerEntry."Entry Type"::Sale);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Posting Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));
      JobLedgerEntry.DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));
      IF JobLedgerEntry.FINDSET THEN
        REPEAT
          CustLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Document No.");
          CustLedgerEntry.SETFILTER(
            "Document Type", '%1|%2', CustLedgerEntry."Document Type"::Invoice, CustLedgerEntry."Document Type"::"Credit Memo");
          CustLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Document No.", JobLedgerEntry."Document No.");
          IF CustLedgerEntry.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
            CustLedgerEntry.CALCFIELDS("Amount (LCY)","Remaining Amt. (LCY)");
            IF CustLedgerEntry."Amount (LCY)" <> 0 THEN BEGIN
              PercDec := (-1 * JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)") / CustLedgerEntry."Amount (LCY)";
              IF JobLedgerEntry."Installment Invoice" THEN
                PayedInstallments := PayedInstallments + (PercDec * (CustLedgerEntry."Amount (LCY)" - CustLedgerEntry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)"))
              ELSE
                PayedCostPlus := PayedCostPlus + (PercDec * (CustLedgerEntry."Amount (LCY)" - CustLedgerEntry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)"))
            END;
          END;
          IF JobLedgerEntry."Installment Invoice" THEN
            InstallmentsToReceive := InstallmentsToReceive + (JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)" * -1)
          ELSE
            CostPlusToReceive := CostPlusToReceive + (JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)" * -1);
        UNTIL JobLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;

      InstallmentsToReceive := InstallmentsToReceive - PayedInstallments;
      CostPlusToReceive := CostPlusToReceive - PayedCostPlus;

      IF NOT ControlProjectCostType.GET(Job."No.", ControlProjectCostType."Cost Type"::Labor) THEN BEGIN
         ControlProjectCostType.INIT;
         ControlProjectCostType."Project No." := Job."No.";
         ControlProjectCostType."Main Project No." := Job."Main Project";
         ControlProjectCostType."Cost Type" := ControlProjectCostType."Cost Type"::Labor;
      END;
      Job.COPYFILTER("Cumulation Filter", ControlProjectCostType."Cumulation Filter");
      Job.COPYFILTER("Project Filter", ControlProjectCostType."Project Filter");
      ControlProjectCostType.CALCFIELDS("Actual Costs");
      LaborCost := ControlProjectCostType."Actual Costs";

      Prognosis.RESET;
      Prognosis.SETRANGE("Project No.", Job."No.");
      Prognosis.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", Job."Prognosis Filter");
      IF NOT Prognosis.FINDFIRST THEN
        Prognosis.INIT;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetRevenue@1100285503(ControlProjectCostObject@1100285502 : Record 11012047) : Decimal;
    VAR
      JobLedgerEntry@1100285500 : Record 11072005;
      JobLocal@1000000000 : Record 11072003;
      TotalPrice@1100285501 : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      IF NOT JobLocal.GET(ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.") THEN
        CLEAR(JobLocal);

      //>> CLP
      //JobLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Job No.","Job Task No.","Entry Type","Posting Date");
      //IF JobLocal."Single/Main/Sub Project" = JobLocal."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
      //  JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.")
      //ELSE
      //<< CLP
        JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Job No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Posting Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));//PeriodFilter);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Global Dimension 2 Code", ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object");
      JobLedgerEntry.SETFILTER("Total Price (LCY)", '<>%1', 0);
      IF JobLedgerEntry.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT

        TotalPrice += JobLedgerEntry."Total Price (LCY)";
      UNTIL JobLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;

      IF TotalPrice <> 0 THEN
        TotalPrice := TotalPrice * -1;
      EXIT(TotalPrice);
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetContractAmount@1100285513(ControlProjectCostObject@1100285501 : Record 11012047) : Decimal;
    VAR
      ProjectPrincipal@1100285500 : Record 11012005;
      ContractAmount@1100285502 : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      ProjectPrincipal.SETRANGE("Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
      ProjectPrincipal.SETRANGE("Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
      ProjectPrincipal.SETRANGE("Cost Object", ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object");
      IF ProjectPrincipal.FINDFIRST THEN
        ContractAmount := ProjectPrincipal."Contract Amount";

      EXIT(ContractAmount);
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetPrognosisRevenue@1100285521(ControlProjectCostObject@1100285500 : Record 11012047) : Decimal;
    VAR
      PrognosisLine@1100285501 : Record 11012035;
      JobLocal@1000000000 : Record 11072003;
      Prognosis@1000000001 : Record 11012034;
      PrognosisLineCC@1000000002 : Record 11128270;
      PrognosisRevenue@1100285502 : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      IF NOT JobLocal.GET(ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.") THEN
        CLEAR(JobLocal);

      IF JobLocal."Forecast Level" = JobLocal."Forecast Level"::"Cost Object" THEN BEGIN
        IF JobLocal."Single/Main/Sub Project" = JobLocal."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
          PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.")
        ELSE
          PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Cost Object",  ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object");
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", Job."Prognosis Filter");
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Cost Type", PrognosisLine."Cost Type"::Revenue);
        IF PrognosisLine.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
          PrognosisRevenue += PrognosisLine."Amount Revenue" + PrognosisLine.Invoiced;//PrognosisLine."Prognosis Revenue";
        UNTIL PrognosisLine.NEXT = 0;

      END ELSE BEGIN
        IF JobLocal."Single/Main/Sub Project" = JobLocal."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
          PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.")
        ELSE
          PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Cost Component Code",  ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", Job."Prognosis Filter");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Cost Type", PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Revenue);
        IF PrognosisLineCC.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
          PrognosisRevenue += PrognosisLineCC."Prognosis Total Revenues";//PrognosisLineCC."Amount Revenue" + PrognosisLineCC.Invoiced;//PrognosisLine."Prognosis Revenue";
        UNTIL PrognosisLineCC.NEXT = 0;

      END;

      EXIT(PrognosisRevenue);
    END;

    PROCEDURE PopulateTemptable@1100285501(VAR JobVar@1100285501 : Record 11072003);
    VAR
      ControlProjectCostObject@1100285500 : Record 11012047;
      ControlProjectCostType@1100285502 : Record 11012046;
      JobLedgerEntry@1100285100 : Record 11072005;
      PrognosisLine@1100525000 : Record 11012035;
      PrognosisLineCC@1000000000 : Record 11128270;
    BEGIN
      //"Project No.","Cost Type","Cost Object"

      ControlProjectCostObject.SETRANGE("Project No.", JobVar."No.");
      IF ControlProjectCostObject.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT

        ControlProjectCostObject.CALCFIELDS(Description);

        IF NOT TEMPControlProjectCostObject.GET(ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.",
                ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type", ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object") THEN BEGIN


          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INIT;
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.TRANSFERFIELDS(ControlProjectCostObject);

          CASE TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type" OF
            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type"::Labor:            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '1';
            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type"::Material:         TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '2';
            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type"::Subcontracting:   TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '3';
            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type"::Plant:            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '4';
            TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type"::Sundry:           TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '5';
          END;
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INSERT;

        END;
      UNTIL ControlProjectCostObject.NEXT = 0;

      JobLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Job No.","Cost Type","Entry Type","Posting Date","Purchase Action");
      IF JobVar."Single/Main/Sub Project" = JobVar."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
        JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", JobVar."No.")
      ELSE
        JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Job No.", JobVar."No.");
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Cost Type", JobLedgerEntry."Cost Type"::Revenues);
      IF JobLedgerEntry.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
        IF NOT TEMPControlProjectCostObject.GET(JobLedgerEntry."Job No.",
             JobLedgerEntry."Cost Type", JobLedgerEntry."Global Dimension 2 Code") THEN BEGIN

          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INIT;
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Project No." := JobLedgerEntry."Job No.";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Main Project No." := "Job Ledger Entry"."Main Project No.";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type" := JobLedgerEntry."Cost Type";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object" := JobLedgerEntry."Global Dimension 2 Code";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '6';
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INSERT;

        END;
      UNTIL JobLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;

      PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", JobVar."No.");
      //PrognosisLine.SETFILTER("Prognosis Date", Job.GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter"));//Job."Prognosis Filter");    //**
      PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Cost Type", PrognosisLine."Cost Type"::Revenue);
      PrognosisLine.SETFILTER("Amount Revenue", '<>%1', 0);
      IF PrognosisLine.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
        IF NOT TEMPControlProjectCostObject.GET(PrognosisLine."Project No.",
             PrognosisLine."Cost Type", PrognosisLine."Cost Object") THEN BEGIN

          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INIT;
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Project No." := PrognosisLine."Project No.";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Main Project No." := PrognosisLine."Main Project No.";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type" := PrognosisLine."Cost Type";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object" := PrognosisLine."Cost Object";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '6';
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INSERT;

        END;

      UNTIL PrognosisLine.NEXT = 0;

      PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Project No.", JobVar."No.");
      PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", JobVar."Prognosis Filter");
      IF PrognosisLineCC.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INIT;
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Project No." := PrognosisLineCC."Project No.";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Main Project No." := PrognosisLineCC."Main Project No.";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Type" := PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type";

          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object" := PrognosisLineCC."Cost Component Code";
          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.Description := PrognosisLineCC."Cost Component Description";

          CASE PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type" OF
            PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Labor:           TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '1';
            PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Material:        TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '2';
            PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Subcontracting:  TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '3';
            PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Plant:           TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '4';
            PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Sundry:          TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '5';
            PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Revenue:         TEMPControlProjectCostObject."Cost Component" := '6';
          END;

          TEMPControlProjectCostObject.INSERT;

      UNTIL PrognosisLineCC.NEXT = 0;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetPrognosisCost@1000000000(ControlProjectCostObject@1100285500 : Record 11012047) : Decimal;
    VAR
      PrognosisLine@1100285501 : Record 11012035;
      JobLocal@1100525000 : Record 11072003;
      PrognosisLineCC@1100525001 : Record 11128270;
      PrognosisCost@1100285502 : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      IF NOT JobLocal.GET(ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.") THEN
        CLEAR(JobLocal);

      IF JobLocal."Forecast Level" = JobLocal."Forecast Level"::"Cost Object" THEN BEGIN
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Main Project No.");
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Cost Object",  ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object");
        PrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", Job."Prognosis Filter");
        IF PrognosisLine.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
          PrognosisCost += PrognosisLine."Prognosis Total Cost";
        UNTIL PrognosisLine.NEXT = 0;

      END ELSE BEGIN
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Project No.");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", ControlProjectCostObject."Main Project No.");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Cost Component Code",  ControlProjectCostObject."Cost Object");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", Job."Prognosis Filter");
        PrognosisLineCC.SETFILTER("Cost Type", '<>%1', PrognosisLineCC."Cost Type"::Revenue);
        IF PrognosisLineCC.FINDSET(FALSE) THEN REPEAT
          PrognosisCost += PrognosisLineCC."Prognosis Total Cost";
        UNTIL PrognosisLineCC.NEXT = 0;
      END;

      EXIT(PrognosisCost);
    END;

    PROCEDURE UpdateEditTransactions@1000000012();
    BEGIN
      IF PrintDetails THEN
        PrintTransactionsEditable := TRUE
      ELSE
        PrintTransactionsEditable := FALSE;
    END;

    BEGIN
    {

      160412 ITERO.PEPF Company name from "Company Information"
      180404 ORANGO.FH Changed caption on Request Page from 'Periodfilter' to 'Ackumulerat t.o.m.'
    }
    END.

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
